summary: A tweak for ECE users who use Alternate Start - Live Another Life which moves the start marker so that the prison torch doesn't interfere with the race menu camera.
descriptionHtml: A tweak for [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951]Enhanced Character Edit[/url] users who use [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/9557]Alternate Start - Live Another Life[/url]. This mod moves the start marker so that the prison torch doesn't interfere with the ECE camera (see screenshots for the difference). That's all that this mod currently does.
author: ciathyza
